				<text x="76" y="16" text-anchor="middle" fill="#e07020" font-size="6" font-family="Quicksand, system-ui, sans-serif">musical</text>
				<text x="76" y="20" text-anchor="middle" fill="#e07020" font-size="4.5" font-family="Quicksand, system-ui, sans-serif" opacity="0.6">CQT (pitch/harmony)</text>
